comments: Banton (TOR) extends his leg into Suggs' (ORL) path and delivers contact that affects his SQBR.
Anthony (ORL) makes marginal contact with VanVleet (TOR) as he dribbles the ball up the court.
Barnes (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Anthony's (ORL) path during the pick.
VanVleet (TOR) makes contact with Carter Jr.'s (ORL) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Anunoby's (TOR) path and absorbs the marginal contact from Anunoby on the drive.
Anunoby (TOR) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Suggs (ORL) that affects his jump shot attempt.
LAR shows Suggs (ORL) makes marginal contact with Anunoby's (TOR) arm during his shooting motion that does not affect his shot near the rim.
Anthony (ORL) makes marginal contact to VanVleet's (TOR) body during his drive that does not affect his SBQR.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path and absorbs the contact on the screen.
Trent Jr. (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Anthony (ORL) in the backcourt.
